{"tid":1400244,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"愈來愈霉 肥蕭終於山窮水盡要賣樓","createTime":"2019-08-03T11:55:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T13:04:12.000Z","uid":115613,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"626e522e52af3ce04f60a71da500b5d773e65de7","tid":1400244,"uid":115613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T11:55:44.000Z","msg":"有「買家墳場盤」稱號的大埔比華利山別墅，連補習天王也中招，賣樓大幅損手離場。消息指萊茵道單號洋房，實用面積2,031方呎，原叫價2,600萬元，有指剛減至2,450萬元沽出，呎價12,063元。土地註冊處資料顯示，該洋房賣方為蕭志勇(Weslie)，即為中文科補習天王蕭源(原名蕭志勇)，於2011年5月向恒地(012)以3,077萬元買單位，曾向發展商旗下財務公司承造二按，現沽貨賬面蝕讓627萬元，若計及釐印費及佣金等開支，料損手約780萬元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20190723/59855559\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190723%2F59855559&d=PwwdVKvQMhnOdjdmHJS5OS9NcCfN%2BV0%2B2kMkFhSspzA%3D&h=9cfccd34\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190723%2F59855559&h=f35c651e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20190723/59855559</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />睇黎佢唔夠水 打官司<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65e4f5ed84d27edb0a3774db26a961b844b10b9e","tid":1400244,"uid":115613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T13:04:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1de77cd8310881a58f0370474e9d07959d53dff8","tid":1400244,"u